Span.Text: Enhance situational awareness and improve incident management by capturing, sharing, and reviewing incident information through the familiar tools and mobile devices you use every day.  Enable mobile policing and speed investigation-led lifecycles by optimising the use of mobile devices, apps, social media, and cloud computing in your day-to-day operations.

ObjectDataModels.Title: Number Plate Recognition Image Place Holder

Span.Text: The device is tapped onto a NFC tag on the evidence bag which writes the evidence information to the tag and creates a record in the evidence store.
The application suggests a number of lenses that can provide relevant information relating to the captured information.
In this case, ANPR data relating to the car being investigated can be quickly visualised over a map to see where the car has been.
Further data sources can be leveraged on the officers device to provide further context to the investigation.
These data sources can be restricted to certain date ranges enabling the officer to spot correlation between different events, example the location of the car and recent burglary crime reports.
